author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at how the prevalence of synthetic content continues to pump into every popular website and how the Internet is poised to be overtaken by bots by the end of this year. Can we reverse it? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The Internet Is Actually Falling Apart...
